title: Son of a Boy Dad: Ep. 40 - My Hands Are Filled With Oil
description:
Son of a Boy Dad: Ep. 40 - My Hands Are Filled With Oil -- Sas & Rone discuss their times in Vegas, Philly, Long Island & Europe, the latest shows and movies they've watched, books they've read, they get to the bottom of a poop bandit case, make plans for the pod in LA, & much more -- Full episodes also available on YouTube -- Thanks for listening/watching!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/sonofaboydad
